			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1476946">
									

<p>I wouldn't say they're <em>my opinions</em>, so much. I personally love AWCY, but it's gotten a lot of backlash lately, and the main criticism has been &quot;There's too many articles where people die and then it just says 'are we cool yet?' at the end&quot;. It's been noticed enough that Sorts went so far as to write <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/stop-asking">a parody tale about skeletons popping out of everything</a> in order to comment on it. I wanted to give AWCY an opportunity for self-reflection.</p>

